CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 11, 1961, pg. 18, reads: "Military Ball Guests - The Aerospace Education Seminar was held at the Hotel Hilton last Saturday night. Shown at the Military Ball are, left to right: Patricia Prattis, ROTC Maj. Rodney Coleman, Howard University, Washington, D. C.; Mae Louise Allen, and Cadet Alvin Scott, Howard University. The affair was presented by the Air Force Association and the Arnold Air Society. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Howard University ROTC student Rodney Coleman holding certificate inscribed "Reserve Officers Association..." at Military Ball during Aerospace Education Seminar, Hilton Hotel
